<http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4656.3.11>
    bibo:endPage "571" ;
    bibo:issue "3" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:pubDate "2019-08-15" ;
    bibo:startPage "545" ;
    bibo:volume "4656" ;
    dc:creator "Quah, Evan S. H.; Grismer, L. Lee; Wood, Perry L.; Thura, Myint Kyaw; Oaks, Jamie R.; Lin, Aung" ;
    dc:date "2019" ;
    dc:title "Discovery of the westernmost population of the genus Ansonia Stoliczka (Anura, Bufonidae) with the description of a new species from the Shan Plateau of eastern Myanmar" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3368949>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3368951>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3368953>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3368945>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3368955> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3368949>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. (A) Paratype of Ansonia kyaiktiyoensis sp. nov. (LSUHC 14067). (B) Hill forest habitat of Ansonia kyaiktiyoensis sp. nov. at Kyaiktiyo, Mon State, Myanmar." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3368949/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3368951>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Dorsum (A) and venter (B) of type series of Ansonia kyaiktiyoensis sp. nov. Paratype (LSUHC 14067) on the left and holotype (LSUHC 14066) on the right." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3368951/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3368953>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. (A) Calling adult male Ansonia inthanon from Doi Inthanon, Chiang Mai, Thailand. (B) Close-up of head of para- type of Ansonia kyaiktiyoensis sp. nov. (LSUHC 14067). Note the markings on the snout and under the eye as indicated by the arrows. (C) Close-up of head of A. inthanon from Doi Inthanon, Chiang Mai, Thailand. Note the absence of markings on the head. (Photographs by Ian Dugdale [A & C] and Evan Quah [B])." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3368953/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3368945>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Maximum likelihood (ML) phylogram for species of the genus Ansonia. Nodal support is indicated by Bayesian posterior probability (BPP) / Ultrafast bootstrap (UFBOOT). Black circles represent nodes supported by a BPP and UFB of 1.00 and 100, respectively. Blue node indicates the Thai-Malay Peninsula clade and red node indicates the Thai-Burmese clade. Species outside of the Thai-Malay Peninsula clade are represented by single tip labels for their lineages." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3368945/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3368955>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Distribution of Ansonia species along the Myanmar-Thai border and the type locality of Ansonia kyaiktiyoensis sp. nov. Star = type locality." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3368955/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

